	igate Anger in KidsThrive
DTSTAMP:20260205T082822Z
DTSTART:20260210T200000Z
DESCRIPTION:Breathing exercises only get you so far\; real progress happens
	 when you understand the root cause of anger. Renee Jain\, founder of GoZe
	n!\, a widely used platform that helps kids build emotional strength\, joi
	ns us to guide parents in understanding their child’s anger\, what’s happe
	ning in the brain during outbursts and how to better respond in the moment
