UID:Dvtn8jlt1OAt4JPsu_fY0
SUMMARY:Bloodworks Northwest Blood Drive at Seattle Central College
DTSTAMP:20260205T082822Z
DTSTART:20260212T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:This Valentine’s Week\, be someone’s type. Give blood\, spread 
	love\, and help save lives.\n\nPatient needs are outpacing donations\, and
	 our local blood supply has reached emergency low levels. To keep up\, Blo
	odwork Northwest has had to bring in blood from other parts of the country
	\, a short-term fix as shortages are happening nationwide.\n\nLocal donors
	 are urgently needed to make sure patients in Pacific Northwest hospitals 
	have access to lifesaving transfusions for cancer treatments\, trauma care
	\, and birth complications.\n\nIf you’re feeling healthy\, show some love 
	and give blood. A small act from you can mean everything to someone else 💕
	\n\n🩸💘 Valentine’s Week Blood Drive Thursday\, Feb 12 Seattle Central Coll
	ege – Room BE-1110 10:00 AM – 4:00 PM\n\nBe someone’s type. Give blood.\n\
	nAppointments can be made at https://donate.bloodworksnw.org/donor/schedul
	es/sponsor\\_code or stop on by!
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/bloodworks-northwest-bloo
	d-drive-at-seattle-central-college/17989011/2026-02-12T00
LOCATION:Seattle Central College\, 1701 Broadway- BE 1110\, Seattle\, WA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT6H
END:VEVENT
